# 1. Overview

The EDECOA EM-402A is an all-in-one hybrid inverter/charger integrating:

- Pure sine wave inverter
- MPPT solar charger
- AC battery charger
- Transfer switch
- UPS functionality

The unit supports:
- solar charging
- grid/generator charging
- battery inversion
- automatic source switching

Primary application:
- off-grid solar ESS
- RV systems
- marine systems
- backup power systems

