# 21. Critical Engineering Observations

## This Unit Is NOT Victron-Class Power Electronics

The inverter is:
- functional
- flexible
- cost effective

But:
- protections are less sophisticated
- charging logic simpler
- thermal management more limited

Compared to:
- Victron
- SMA
- Outback
- Schneider

---

## The MPPT Is Very Powerful

110A MPPT at 24V:
- substantial charging capability

Potential solar power into battery:
- >2.5kW continuous

This is significant for:
- your 320Ah CATL bank

---

## Default Lithium Settings Are NOT Optimal for Longevity

Factory defaults:
- push LiFePO4 fairly hard

We will later optimize:
- absorb voltage
- float voltage
- low voltage cutoffs
- source switching thresholds

for:
- cycle life
- reduced stress
- better balancing behavior

---

## Equalization Must Be Disabled

Critical:
- NEVER equalize LiFePO4

Programs 33–39:
- disable entirely

---

## Float Voltage Needs Special Attention

LiFePO4 does not like:
- prolonged high float

We will likely lower:
- float voltage significantly

compared to defaults.

---

## High PV Voltage Requires Care

450V PV max:
- dangerous voltage class

Proper:
- breakers
- disconnects
- grounding
- cable sizing

are extremely important.

---

